<p style="text-align: center;">
	<img alt="Kết quả hình ảnh cho chùa Songzanlin" src="https://cdn02.static-adayroi.com/resize/608_430/100/0/2017/08/07/1502096518122_9260606.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">
